{"tid":2150670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【旺角騷亂】事隔逾4年再有1男被起訴暴動罪 待轉介區院審","createTime":"2020-08-11T04:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T05:36:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b6028d415a11f4f46524a04e2cc1f231a25a861","tid":2150670,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8014&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lKpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=93545671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8014</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官 #新案件<br />\n👤陳(28) #旺角騷亂<br />\n<br />\n被告被控於2016年2月9日連同他人參與暴動。控方申請押後，以轉介文件到區域法院。<br />\n<br />\n本案押後至8月31日0930，於西九龍裁判法院一庭答辯。<br />\n<br />\n🟢期間被告以現有條件擔保，新增3項條件：<br />\n1 被告不得離港<br />\n2 於指定地址居住<br />\n3 交出旅遊證件<br />\n考慮到被告身體狀況，毋須報到。"},{"pid":"6aeffade538c77c878cd2fa1942cd82c3a5b829b","tid":2150670,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3aa91954d9a3bd8ed1a378c9251747bfe1a4e8","tid":2150670,"uid":201656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea19445651d1b627de983dc4bdf48d0c3540cff2","tid":2150670,"uid":201656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd345108eb0f8620703eb79e77217af439e0cf26","tid":2150670,"uid":201656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e24ee1